<PageLayout title={`${title} | Better Lives Building Tribes`} schema={schema} description="You have been considering therapy for loneliness, isolation, or difficulty connecting with others. Your therapist suggests group therapy. Your first thought is \"Absolutely not.\" The idea of being vuln">
